Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.44,0:01:38.80,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}把这样的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:42.02,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}吹き飛ばすきっかけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.85,0:01:42.02,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}全部吹飞的契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:45.92,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}招くばかりの指先を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:45.92,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}吸引而来的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:49.84,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}手のひらで重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:49.84,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}重叠在手掌之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.45,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}今を変えることは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.45,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}改变现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.94,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}辛いこともあるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.94,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}虽然是件痛苦的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.87,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}たとえピースが揃っても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.87,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}就算Piece全部集齐
