Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:03.89,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}也得用这双手去指引
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.61,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}大事な今を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.61,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}把重要的现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:10.08,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}手放すのは怖いよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:10.08,OPCN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,100)\blur1}放手离去是很可怕的吧
